      </p>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0658P0-03404'>
        <a name='S5LV0658P0_20040301_GCR_193'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-john-whitty' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0658P0_20040301_GCR_193' title='Link to this speech by Mr John Whitty' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
