            Therefore, I am very grateful to the Government for what they are doing in the Bill to ensure that the additional costs which occur in areas such as the
            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_194gc' title='Col. 194GC &mdash; HL Deb 01 March 2004 vol 658 c194GC' name='column_194gc' href='#column_194gc' rel='bookmark'>194GC</a>
